      <property name="text">
       <string>Welcome to The Quest of No Return.

Explore the ancient Egyptian temple, collect clue fragments, and reach the sacred Ankh before time runs out.

MOVEMENT
• Use WASD keys to move through the temple.
• Explore every corner to find hidden treasures.

CLUE FRAGMENTS
• Each room contains 3 glowing clue fragments.
• Walk near them to collect (they pulse gold).
• Collect all 3 to activate the room's altar.

THE ALTAR
• After collecting 3 clues, the altar glows.
• Press E at the altar to face a riddle.
• Answer correctly to advance to the next room.

TORCHES &amp; RELICS
• Light torches with E to reveal hidden relics.
• Relics are bonus collectibles that boost your score.

STATUES &amp; TABLETS
• Press E near statues for ancient lore.
• Tablets provide hints for riddles.

GUARDIANS
• Mummies, scarabs, and spectres patrol the halls.
• Some will chase you if you get too close!
• Avoid them or lose a life.

ROOM HAZARDS
• Spike traps activate in cycles - time your movement.
• Collapsing floors give way beneath you.
• Fake doors are deadly traps in disguise.

BOSS FIGHT
• Khonshu guards the final chamber.
• Dodge his crescent projectiles.
• Attack with R when he's tired (after 8 shots).
• Hide behind destructible cover for safety.

LIVES &amp; TIMER
• Contact with enemies or traps costs lives.
• If all lives are lost or time runs out, you fail.

GOAL
• Survive all 7 chambers and claim the sacred Ankh!</string>
